{"tid":2390218,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你棟大廈強制檢疫嘅機率係","createTime":"2021-02-01T11:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T08:18:43.000Z","uid":93050,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5e08fbfa21761a9cfc821ac6a4eed28c8208c7","tid":2390218,"uid":93050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:55:54.000Z","msg":"視乎大廈人數，保守估計如果全港有<span class=\"x-large\">兩萬人</span>感染，你棟大廈有<strong>500人</strong>，強制檢疫嘅機率係<span class=\"large\">73.65%</span>。<br />\n<br />\n假設感染嘅人係randomly distributed among 全香港嘅大廈，我用geometric distribution 嘅formula 計，一個人感染嘅機率就係兩萬/七百五十萬，姐係 p = 0.27%，無感染嘅機率係 99.73% （1-0.27%）。<br />\n<br />\n不過，成棟大廈計嘅話，一個case 都無嘅機率就係99.73% to the power of 大廈人數，如果大廈有500 人，無事嘅機率就係99.73%^ 500 = 26.35%。所以強制檢疫嘅機率係73.65%。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以對返，如果你大廈得50 人，恭喜你，強制檢疫嘅機率就只係12.5%<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DiN5ncd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDiN5ncd.png&h=875eb0c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55ec12b5b814f7f620d87773c8509017ecb7b1e7","tid":2390218,"uid":49136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T21:26:53.000Z","msg":"有啲公屋一層幾十戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cd8fdb97b448c4c2977ffe6850e9b60d549183","tid":2390218,"uid":134683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T21:31:37.000Z","msg":"明明就係二分一機會率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b195f1c05b2d26b3ee29c927ca49d96a4cf7b2","tid":2390218,"uid":300782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T21:35:43.000Z","msg":"100%"},{"pid":"c8d6f20af37955cb9f1e439c01ead0346ab8a2d7","tid":2390218,"uid":240004,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T22:22:17.000Z","msg":"目的就係拎晒你所有香港人DNA<br />\n就算計到1%都只係遲早既事"},{"pid":"e7d5ee801829429bc6c497b304cd181c0b7b88bf","tid":2390218,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T22:23:15.000Z","msg